Ross Garon - Point72 Asset Management












































 
 

 













Facebook




Twitter




Google




LinkedIn


 







Select Page


  
 
 








Leadership
Return to Leadership
 
 




Ross Garon
 

  

Ross Garon is a Managing Director at Point72 Asset Management, L.P., and the head of Cubist Systematic Strategies, LLC, the Firm’s Quant business.
Before Point72, Mr. Garon was the Co-Founder and Managing Member of Tykhe Capital LLC. He began his career in quantitative finance at D. E. Shaw & Co in New York, London and Tokyo.  He  also served as head of global business management at Commerzbank’s equities division.
Mr. Garon graduated magna cum laude from Harvard University. He serves on the Boards of Neighborhood Trust and the Andrew Goodman Foundation, the Steering Committee of ITBB, and the Editorial Board of the Journal of Investment Strategies.
 
 
 
 
 

 
 
 
 
 
 

















